snippet.textDisplay:
Interesting how no one saw or hear anything except for Rudiger which is why they never found out “who” did it. There’s no proof whatsoever. And Rudiger isn’t exactly the most honest person considering he milked that pathetic “foul” to get Son sent off a minute before the supposed racism happened. However, a Chelsea supporter was arrested at the game for racially abusing Son. Why aren’t we talking about that? No Chelsea or Tottenham player heard or saw anything either and we’re living in a time where everyone is surveilled which is how they caught the Chelsea supporter for his racial abuse of Son. Moreover, Tottenham supporters don’t have a history of racism either unlike Chelsea supporters. In fact, Tottenham was one of the top five areas in the UK with the highest Stay votes.

In addendum, Rudiger claimed racism before and Roma launched an investigation into it. Conclusion: they found nothing.
